ActAn Act to amend the Federal-Provincial Fiscal Arrangements Act and to make consequential amendments to other Acts (fiscal equalization payments to the provinces and funding to the territories)
PrecisOrder fixing APRIL 1, 2006 as the day on which subsections 4.1(3) and 4.92(3) of the Federal-Provincial Fiscal Arrangements Act, as enacted by subsection 1(1) of this Act [BILL C-24], being chapter 7 of the Statutes of Canada, 2005, shall COME INTO FORCE.
